Initial Data Management Plan
As agreed upon in the amended contract, I am currently on an unpaid leave (while 
completing the Marie Curie Individual Fellowship) until August 2023. Therefore, I have not 
started the project of the FWO proposal yet. Once I start the project, I will submit the initial, 
intermediate and final DMP.
